cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on language learning through interactive multimodal communication between agents. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the use of neural networks for learning and the need for cooperative behavior suggest that cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Learning) are also likely categories. The paper also discusses the importance of ensuring that agents do not develop an adhoc communication code, which suggests a connection to cs.SD (Sound) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) for developing more robust communication systems.
